The rulers of the Lostbelts? I respect them, of course.
After all, each and every one of them yielded to Chaldea.
So wise, so mature, those kings and queens!
Oh, but...don't lump me in with them.
They're just a bunch of wretched losers. I, on the other hand, actually accomplished what I set out to do.
I wanna put my skills to the test. How 'bout it!?
Ibaraki seems to really like sweet candies... Fufu, but I bet she doesn't  know what I think is the sweetest.
Alas, we meet again Jeanne incarnate! Let us celebrate by consuming the evils of the sea.

That anger is truly my sin.
You, the queen of victory.

Huh!? I sense something... BB's embarrassing fetishes, the dark past that I thought I had cut out and thrown away... The Sakura Five...!?
But does it look like they had a change of heart!?
Whoa... Even the Alter Egos grow psychologically, but I am still the super cute little devil...
The original girl I'm based off of must have been such a handful.

Chaldea is full of strong fighters. Very nice!
All right, let's do this. I'm going to get serious.
Let's have a match!

Hektor?
I guess it's good that he's on our side. It'll be a pain if he's our enemy. I would never instigate...
Ouch!
Hektor, you bastard! What's the big idea throwing a rock at me!?
Fine! Let's have another duel!
Hey, hold still and let me spear you!

Hm? Oh? Hmmm...?
I think I may have seen this girl in the past... Or not...
There's a resemblance...I think...?
Passionlip is probably a little dangerous. If she pulls a surprise attack, even I would wind up getting turned into a cube...

I love generous, fearless heroes who don't get jealous!
They do exist, right? Summon one for me right now!

Hey, kid. Yeah, I'm talking to you, kid.
Don't stay out too late. Come back before the sun sets.
Got it? GOT IT???
So you have a sister too! Fine, then. As a special treat, I'll be your friend. You should be happy about that.

I had no idea how things would turn out once Alter appeared, but the original Okita is the tried and true one. There's no time to be bothered with Alter...and by the way, what do you think of this swimsuit?
I'm sure you can appreciate its greatness, since you're my Alter and all!
Eh? You want to wear it too!? Listen, it took a LOT of work over a LONG time to get to wear one of these babies!
I have detected a fallen hero. I ask that you permit me to invite them to Valhalla, Master.

Huh? Teach?
Didn't they call him the last pirate after I died?
Of course I'd take notice of him.
But then again, look at him... Honestly I'm relieved. It's good to know that no matter how much time passes, pirates will always be scum!

Okay, nope! Nope, nope!
That old swordsmith man is...I don't how to explain it, but all of my nope!
I can't put a finger on it, but my body gets all restless and my facial expressions get real tense, yet I can't keep my eyes off him. Maybe it's just that we're not compatible?
Don't tell me...is he connected to Shiva? Is that why my body is instinctually on guard?
Whatever the reason, there's no way I can interact with him.
Bye!

Oh, there's that biker Heroic Spirit.
That's quite the monster machine... Maybe I'll invite him to a race next time.
But what's his True Name...?
Oh, Golden?
Is there really a Heroic Spirit by that name?

Sooo cute!
Oh my, oh my! I cannot believe it!
They are all such lovely and adorable Heroic Spirits!
Ooh, I can't help but to squeeze them so tightly!
...Oh dear. Giving them candy isn't enough!
I'm going to borrow your kitchen for a bit! I'm going to make them many delicious things!

Hm, I like how determined you appear.
All right. Let's do this.

How beautiful...
What a lovely maiden. I can see why she left a mark on history.
Oh no, no, no. This is no good.
A damsel mustn't be left out on her own in danger, and any knight who permitted this to happen would surely have his reputation tarnished.
And so, Master...
I shall go fulfill my knightly duties... Understood?

Mr. Sakamoto? I did see him a few times back in the day when we were in Kyoto.
After all, the Shinsengumi was also after him. But Mr. Sakamoto was too quick and he kept eluding us...
Either way, we're now fighting on the same side, so let's work well together.
By the way, that woman who keeps tagging along with him...
Eh? Noble Phantasm? What does that actually mean?

Other gods have come too, it seems.
I believe in freedom, but too much freedom can be troubling...

Do you have a moment, lovely lady passing my way?
If you have some time to spare, would you care to spend it with me?
In modern terms, you'd call what I'm doing hitting on women.

Oh, it's Papa. He's up to something bad again?
Good grief, you're a grown man, don't you have even a bit of shame? ...You don't?
I see.

Hm, there seems to be a slew of strong warriors here.
I would like to ask to duel with them...
But I suppose such an all-out match between swordsmen is frowned upon, right?

H-h-how shameless!
Absolutely not, absolutely not!
Now you listen, y-y-you must be more modest than that!
Unacceptable, unacceptable!

What about any children born outside Europe, you ask?
They are...let's see...they are like my descendants' friends!
Come, all! You're all sweeties!

L-L-L-L-L-Lord Tawara Touta!?
Th-the legend himself! Wh-wh-wh-what should I do, Master!?
Is asking for an autograph and a handshake allowed in Chaldea!?

Chaldea is full of strong fighters. Very nice!
All right, let's do this. I'm going to get serious.
Let's have a match!

What about any children born outside Europe, you ask?
They are...let's see...they are like my descendants' friends!
Come, all! You're all sweeties!
There's a ton of cute reptile girls!!! I want to fondle them so much! I want to dig up their weak points!

The Knights of the Round table are in this world too. That must mean there's another me in this world.
One day, I'd like to meet this other me.

Hmph. There are quite a lot of Romans around here.
I just hope they are not so weak as Valerian or foolish as Gallienus...

All the Swordbeauties are dangerous.
Honestly...
No, I suppose that's how they are supposed to be.

Oooh.
Look at you, all dressed up. You look good, Ibaraki. I'm happy for you.
I think we could form some sort of duo now.
That's right...the two of us.
Fufu. Come now, don't go running in circles, all excited like that. Careful not to trip, okay?

In the Servant Universe, I hear there's someone who looks like me.
Cocoa-colored skin and a rainbow sword...
I hear photon rays dance around like powdered snow, and she leads the galaxy to its end.
...Hmmm, is that really me?
I feel like the latter half took a dark turn...
I wanna put my skills to the test. How 'bout it!?

I see that there are a handful of other Servants who, like me, have animal companions here in Chaldea. But I have to say Yatsufusa and I are the best pair! He's the biggest, cutest... Er...
Well, he may not be the biggest... Cutest...may be up for debate...
He's comfortable to ride...no, sometimes I strain my back after riding him...
Oh come on, don't pout.
Ah I know! He's the best at gathering wild mountain plants! That's it!

Whoa, it's you, Roland!
Sorry, I didn't notice you since you were wearing clothes. Well yeah...you do normally wear clothes, but...but your less usual appearance makes a stronger impression...
Even if I've only met you when you were wearing clothes, your legend is just too much...

The legendary King Arthur...
I had...
No idea...
They were a woman!

The older witch... I-I mean, ScÃ¡thach-Skadi.
I don't know why, but I'm inclined to call her Mother...

This Noble Phantasm was developed to defeat a certain genius swordsman who crossed my path in my life once.
Ah
So you have a sister too! Fine, then. As a special treat, I'll be your friend. You should be happy about that.

Hey! You're Achilles, with the weak heel! I'm also vulnerable to a strike on the underside of my legs. We're like twins! What's that? We're not the same?
I guess...
Jousting! Let's do it!

Touta?
The Great Sage... Heaven's Equal...?
No.
But he's still. A good disciple.

An Indian Heroic Spirit is here!
Wonderful. India is like a second home to me... No, it's more like my soul's home.
I do so hope we can become friends!

Seeing their faces reminds me of the sea voyage I took back then.
I just boarded as the ship's doctor, so I didn't have time to think whether it was fun or not...
Well, at least I was never bored.

I don't believe this... I never imagined I'd ever get a chance to meet the King of Conquerors at that age...
Now hold on, Alexander! That's enough of the Protection of Zeus for now!
That poor child. The Allfather's curse still torments her.

All children born on the European continent, on the great land of Europa, are my descendants.
What good children you all are!

Hey you. Yes, you, I'm talking to you.
My Christmas present, the roulette, is broken. Exchange it for me.
Cooling-off period?
Huh, what? It's already over?
Don't screw with me!

Ugh. There're so many other swimsuit Servants, aren't there?
Do I...do I fall short? Do they beat me in attractiveness?
I'm not inferior to them, am I? Am I!? AM I!?
I don't fall short?
Poggers!

Today's snack is a specially made cake!
Come on children, go wash your hands and come and get it!

Your attention please, good boys and girls! It's time for a magic trick!
Now take a good look at this silk hat. Lo and behold, a dove...
...A dove...
I-I-I-I mean, lo and behold, an angel appears!
There's absolutely no trickery here!
...Where did that dove go?

Jeanne d'Arc Alter Santa Lily.
So she's my Lily predecessor. I know of her.
Her Noble Phantasm seems fun, and both my Alter predecessor and I want to doff our hats in respect...on the inside.

Are you...are you...a mechanical Servant!?
Oh my...
U-um, if you don't mind...um...may I...have a word...with you...?

Ah, Jeanne d'Arc, it's you.
It's almost time for prayer. Would you like to join me?

I feel bad for Medea.
She's such an idiot, all because she neglected Hecate's herbalism techniques.
Poor child.
I'm...really...jealous...
His operas are nice.
Ah, DantÃ¨s. Fwahahaha. I imagine it is quite a surprise for you, one who uses evil to achieve justice, to see someone like me here! Hey! Hello? Answer me!

How beautiful...
What a lovely maiden. I can see why she left a mark on history.
Oh no, no, no. This is no good.
A damsel mustn't be left out on her own in danger, and any knight who permitted this to happen would surely have his reputation tarnished.
And so, Master...
I shall go fulfill my knightly duties... Understood?

My fairy-tale friends... I call them fair friends for short.
The more friends connected to fairy tales Cinderella Elisabeth makes, the stronger she gets.
That information is sure to be useful for you!

I can't stand that white knight, the Saber who claims to be X's disciple...
Just the thought of it makes me hungry to the core... I couldn't resist, so I just hopped on Galactic Amazonu and ordered some strawberry daifuku delivered via sub-light flight.

All children born on the European continent, on the great land of Europa, are my descendants.
What good children you all are!
...By the way...I recognize...that face...
Jousting! Let's do it!

Ah...I am not fond of that type of king...
I must take caution not to be killed...

Ah, so you're Da Vinci...
No, don't worry about it.
But...yeah...
All I want to say is that I wish you good health as long as fate allows.

What about any children born outside Europe, you ask?

Come, all! You're all sweeties!

What the... An oni warrior puppet! I see now...Chinzei Hachirou, or rather Minamoto-no-Tametomo! Hah!
Tsukuyomi Revolving Cannon, Gouchin Yumiharizuki? Wieldin' a sword's smart and all, but wieldin' a bow looks good, too! Maybe I'll shoot for Archer-class next manifestation.

Castor:, Sister, we joined in some adventures aboard that ship, didn't we?
Pollux:, Yes we did, Brother. Heracles was indeed a great soldier.
Castor:, He sure was... Wait a minute. Have you been meeting up with Heracles without me?
Pollux:, You have the wrong idea. I'll kill you, Brother.

I envy you, Koyo.
You look terrifying, but you're still very trustworthy.
Why? Well...because...my instincts tell me...
Huh. Actually, I don't know why.
Maybe because you look like someone I know...?

It may not be my place to say this, but...a Foreigner?
My understanding is that consorting with Servants of that sort is dangerous.
And I sense something especially sinister from that Abigail girl. A remote universe beyond even the Buddha's reach... I cannot help but to be intrigued...
Oh, no, I am absolutely not saying that because I am envious of her swimsuit that absolutely screams cute!""

They may not resemble or act the same way, but whenever I see boys of that age...
Well, it brings me back.
Hm? Are they eating apples?
Hey Master. It's okay for them to bite it, but tell them not to put it on top of their heads.
Just watching them makes my heart rate go up.

How beautiful...
What a lovely maiden. I can see why she left a mark on history.
Oh no, no, no. This is no good.

I shall go fulfill my knightly duties... Understood?
Don'tcha think there's a bunch of roughneck womenfolk around here? It's scary! Someone just grabbed me by the chest! All I did was give them a funny look!

All the oni who assembled on Mt. Ooe...
These oni are truly terrifying...
Please be careful, Master. Oni are not human. Even if they raid your home or flay your flesh, you should be grateful so long as you survive the encounter.

Hmmm...
I do not know why I feel restless.
I feel a tingling sensation... It is almost as if someone is staring intently at me. Perhaps it is someone who wants to protect the world's morality with me, but is shyly hiding in the bushes!

I once stayed in the Sparrow's Inn. I will never forget the hospitality I received from that lovely proprietress. One of these days, we should all stay at that inn to heal our wounds and recover from our fatigue!

Okita Souji... The other me.
I don't have much memory left of living as Okita Souji, and so sometimes I question whether I'm really her counterpart.
This might be off-topic, but for some reason I'm taller and bustier than her. Did I maybe have a growth spurt?

I don't like gods.
Doesn't matter if they're old or new...they never do anything good.
Hey Master, can I kill them?

What about any children born outside Europe, you ask?
They are...let's see...they are like my descendants' friends!
Come, all! You're all sweeties!

Ah, you are from that one time...
If you don't mind, please let me take a photograph again. For the sake of keeping record of our daily lives.

Prince of Lan Ling...? Whoa, he's definitely something to behold.
Makes sense that his looks are so legendary.
Eh? I give him a run for his money?
Hahaha! You've got good taste, Master!

So that is my architect...
I never thought to be reunited after all this time.
I see...with a body like that, attaining the pinnacle of performance in humanoid form is likely possible.
It pleases me to see that my design became helpful in the future.

Do you have a moment, lovely lady passing my way?
If you have some time to spare, would you care to spend it with me?
In modern terms, you'd call what I'm doing hitting on women.

Baobhan Sith...High Queen Morgan's daughter.
And, my colleague.
...I've always known her to be a wanton killer, but I have no right to criticize her folly...
Beneath it all, we're cut from the same cloth.

Okay, what's the first thing you do when you come back from Rayshifting?
Have you forgotten what Miss Nightingale told you to do?
That's right! Wash your hands and gargle. Good, you're so wonderful!
...Oh. So you're a king.

What a lovely maiden. I can see why she left a mark on history.

Oh, King of Knights, you have a good appetite.
Here, keep eating.
I have an infinite amount of rice.

That cat-eared girl is Tamamo Cat!?
I don't like her. She ruined my plans to build a ranch. Well, I do like her Noble Phantasm, though. It's only human to get sleepy after a hard day's work, you know!
Oh, by the way, Master, are you interested in running a cafe?
I see great potential in that girl's second and third costumes... What do you think?

...Standing shoulder to shoulder with that man?
While promising, it also invites inevitable conflict. This is the first time Iâ€™ve ever felt this way. In any case, this is the ideal my mother wished for. I'll try it out, for now.

I know logically that we're not in the mountains, but...I can't help but get riled up.
Argh! I got no other choice! You there. You think you're strong, right? Then let's sumo wrestle!

Many humans may have reached godhood, but I never imagined I would ever meet a human who surpassed gods.
Actually, hold on a minute...
Her mental structure can't even be expressed in hyper dimensions! What the heck...she's making an entire universe in her stomach!?

They are...let's see...they are like my descendants' friends!
Come, all! You're all sweeties!
Ah, what a feast for my eyes. These swimsuits are truly good...

Who knew Echigo's god of war was a woman...
Then again, even Lord Nobunaga's a woman here, so I guess there's no reason to be surprised anymore.
You know, any normal person would be shocked by this stuff though.
Well, Okita was also thought to be male...

I do hope Yang Guifei feels the same way too...

A-a Knight of the Round Table!
The proud and noble knights of King Arthur!
Wow... This is so amazing, Master!

Now be good. Don't move.
